WEBVTT

00:02:58.855 --> 00:03:02.808
You could tell that Rich felt guilty

00:03:03.792 --> 00:03:07.577
that this factory
was closing on his watch.

00:03:11.768 --> 00:03:14.522
What hit me the hardest at that time

00:03:15.442 --> 00:03:18.571
was that this wasn't just an old factory.

00:03:19.173 --> 00:03:20.773
This was a time machine.

00:03:21.836 --> 00:03:26.408
This is where people built lives,
they left for wars,

00:03:26.432 --> 00:03:29.260
they bragged about home runs
and report cards.